#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Uducamurongo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "You always move first."
msgstr "Buri gihe Itangira . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If on your turn you cannot outflank and flip at least one opposing stone, "
"your turn is forfeited and your opponent moves again. However, if a move is "
"available to you, you may not forfeit your turn."
msgstr ""
"ku na Guhindukiza Ku Rimwe DISIKI , ni na Nanone . , NIBA A Himura ni Bihari "
"Kuri , Gicurasi OYA . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A stone may outflank any number of stones in one or more rows in any number "
"of directions at the same time - horizontally, vertically or diagonally. A "
"row is defined as one or more stones in a continuous straight line."
msgstr ""
"A DISIKI Gicurasi Icyo ari cyo cyose Umubare Bya in Rimwe Cyangwa Birenzeho "
"Urubariro: in Icyo ari cyo cyose Umubare Bya Ku i Igihe - Mu buryo "
"Butambitse , Mu buryo buhagaze Cyangwa . A Urubariro ni Nka Rimwe Cyangwa "
"Birenzeho in A Gikomeza Umurongo: . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may not skip over your own color stone to outflank an opposing stone."
msgstr "Gicurasi OYA Gusimbuka KURI Ibara: DISIKI Kuri DISIKI . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stones may only be outflanked as a direct result of a move and must fall in "
"the direct line of the stone placed down."
msgstr ""
"Gicurasi Nka A Igisubizo Bya A Himura na in i Umurongo: Bya i DISIKI Hasi . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All stones outflanked in any one move must be flipped, even if it is to the "
"player's advantage not to flip them."
msgstr ""
"in Icyo ari cyo cyose Rimwe Himura , ATARIIGIHARWE NIBA ni Kuri i OYA Kuri "
"Guhindukiza . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a stone is placed on a square, it can never be moved to another square "
"later in the game."
msgstr "A DISIKI ni ku A kare , Nta na rimwe Kuri kare Nyuma in i &Game . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it is no longer possible for either player to move, the game is over. "
"Stones are then counted and the player with the majority of his or her color "
"discs on the board is declared the winner."
msgstr ""
"ni Oya ya:  Kuri Himura , i &Game ni KURI . Hanyuma na i Na: i Bya Cyangwa "
"Ibara: ku i ni i . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "It is possible for a game to end before all 64 squares are filled."
msgstr "ni ya:  A &Game Kuri Impera Mbere Byose 64 kare Byuzuye . "

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to place stones on the corners whenever possible. Your opponent cannot "
"outflank these stones."
msgstr "Kuri ku i . . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Avoid placing stones on one of the three neighbor fields of a corner unless "
"you are absolutely sure that your opponent will not be able to put a stone "
"on a corner."
msgstr ""
"ku Rimwe Bya i Amashami: Bya A Inguni OYA Kuri Gushyira A ku A Inguni . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Sometimes it is better to offer some stones to your opponent."
msgstr "ni Kuri Kuri "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Try to put stones on fields which prevent your opponent from moving."
msgstr "Kuri Gushyira ku Amashami: Kuva: Kwimura . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to force your opponent to put a stone in a neighboring field of a corner."
msgstr "Kuri Gushyiraho Ingufu Kuri Gushyira A in A Umwanya Bya A Inguni . "

